Take a temporary string "abc" and count the number of insertions to make it a valid string.
**For Ex:- string word = "abb"**

a b b **(i pointer)**
|----------->    same character increment i and j by 1.
abc  **(j pointer)**

a b b
--|----------->  same character increment i and j by 1.
-abc

a b b
----|-----------> Not same increment j  and count by 1. count = 1
-abc

a b b
----|-----------> Not same increment j  and count by 1. count = 2
----abc
a b b
----|-----------> same character increment i and j by 1.
---abc

**return count+3-j;**


