Using Stack datastructure .
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
ans=0
  Read each char from string 
1 if char is 'a' then 
    if  stack is empty or top is 'c'  then push 'a' 
    else if top is 'b' then increment ans by 1 and push 'c' and 'a'.
    else if top is 'a' then increment ans by 2 and push 'b' and 'c'.

2 if char is 'b' then
   if stack is empty or top is 'c' then increnment ans by 1 push 'a' and 'b'.
    else if top is 'a' then push 'b'.
    else if top is 'b' then increment ans by 2 and push 'c'and 'a'.

3  if char is 'c' then
    check similarly and increment the ans

after completion of loop (the last char should be ends with 'c')
 if top of the stack is a then increment the ans by 2 
 else if top of the stack is b then increment the ans by 1

return ans;



# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity:O(n)
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

# Code
```
class Solution {
    public int addMinimum(String s) {
        Stack<Character> st=new Stack<>();
        int max=0;
        for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++)
        {
            if(s.charAt(i)=='a')
            {
            if(st.isEmpty()||st.peek()=='c')
            {
              st.push(s.charAt(i));
            }
            else if(st.peek()=='b')
            {
              max++;
                st.push('c');
                st.push(s.charAt(i));
            }
            else if(st.peek()=='a')
            {
                max+=2;
                st.push('b');
                st.push('c');
                st.push(s.charAt(i));
            }
            }
            else if(s.charAt(i)=='b')
            {
                  if(st.isEmpty()||st.peek()=='c')
                  {
                      max++;
                      st.push('a');
                    st.push(s.charAt(i));
                  }
                 else if(st.peek()=='a')
                  {
                    st.push(s.charAt(i));
                  }
                 else if(st.peek()=='b')
                 {
                    max+=2;
                    st.push('c');
                    st.push('a');
                   st.push(s.charAt(i));
                 }
            }
            else {
                 if(st.isEmpty()||st.peek()=='c')
                  {
                      max+=2;
                      st.push('a');
                      st.push('b');
