# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
us1 will give unqiue element count for the prefix part and us2 will give unique element count for suffix part. Since, in answer we want prefix-suffix, prefix part's count is added and suffix's count is subtracted. The reason of subtracting before inserting to us2 is because suffix part starts from i+1.

