This approach is not working for test case -> 6,9,8 and k = 1
the ans should be 31 and my code is giving 30... 
to get answer we multiply 8 by 2 so array will be [6,9,16]

the dp code is not taking 9|16 (25) as return value instead it is taking 18|8 (26) which is wrong.
this is happening because we are maximising our answer in aur recursive code and it is taking 26 as our final value instead of 25 (which gives us the right answer).


# Wrong Code
