# Approach
 Optimised dp,
 where dp[i][j] is maximum OR after using j operation till index i


# Code
```
class Solution {
    public long maximumOr(int[] nums, int k) {
        long dp[] = new long[k+1];
        long tmp[] = new long[k+1];

        for(long xx:nums){
            for(int i=0;i<=k;i++){
                long max=0;
                for(int j=0;j<=i;j++){
                    max = Math.max(max, (xx<<j)|dp[i-j] );
                }
                tmp[i] = max;
            }
            dp = tmp;
            tmp = new long[k+1];
        }
        return dp[k];

    }
}
```

