# Intuition
We have to multiply by 2 to only one number k times. so we can multiply 2 (k times) for each number one by one, and then take OR of whole array and maximize answer.

# Approach
We have to multiply 2^k(multiply 2 k times) to each number one by one and maximize answer. for doing this brute force solution goes O(N^2). for O(N) time complexity we can use prefix and sufffix OR of the array, by doing this we can calculate OR of whole array where one changing element (i.e. the element we have multiplied by 2^k) in O(1) time complexity.

