# Intuition
We need to make the string palindrome. Thus we need to compare first and last indices.

# Approach
- **(step 1)** Keep one index at beginning of string and other at the end.
- **(case 1)** Update the first index to the character at last index if last index character is alphabetically smaller.
- **(case 2)** Else update last index character to first index character.
- **(step 3)** Increment and decrement the first and last indexes.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n)
