## While loop with two pointers
![image.png](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/69bea62f-bb8b-4854-9d4c-567789c77797_1691480782.9002447.png)

```
class Solution:
    def makeSmallestPalindrome(self, s: str) -> str:
        left = 0
        right = len(s) - 1
        while left < right:
            if s[left] != s[right]:
                ch = min(s[left], s[right])
                s = s[:left] + ch + s[left + 1:right] + ch + s[right + 1:]
            left += 1
            right -= 1
        return s
```

