# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Iterate till half of the array(excluding the n/2 th element), check if those aren't equal. If not, then if `ith` is greater than `(n-1-i)th` then change `ith` to minimum of `ith` and `(n-1-i)th` else change the last one with minimum of those.
