# Intuition
**``` Since the constraints are minimal 🙃🙃we can try out for all possible substrings, check if the substring if there in the dictionary and then update the cost.```
```At last minimize the cost after trying all possiblities```**

# Approach
**```Since we are trying for all possible substrings we can use Recursion and then Memoize the overlapping subproblems.```**
# Time Complexity
**``` O(N^2) as for every index we are tyring for all elements where N is the size of array```**
# Space Complexity
**``` O(N) for DP table which is used to memoize the overlapping subproblems  ```**

