# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
dp[i][j]: min amount of chars left for s[i..j)
At each step try every word in the dict, and if it's found we can break it into two subproblems.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
O(n^2) states, transitions take O(d*n)
So in total around O(n^4)

- Space complexity:
